WrappedRangeDBIDByLookup.Linear
    public interface RangeSearcher<O>
    The interface for range queries, that can return all objects within the specified radius.

    Do not confuse this with rectangular window queries, which are also sometimes called "range queries".

    Since:
    0.4.0
    Author:
    Erich Schubert
